\n．<strong><span class=\"red\">香港特別行政區參與國家事務的</span></strong>貢獻及<strong><span class=\"red\">受惠</span></strong>：國家支持香港發展的政策；香港在不同範疇推動內地發展及交流；捐款賑災或支援內地發展中地區的需要<br />\n<br />\n2.改革開放以來的國家 （45&ndash;50 小時）<br />\n【改革開放與人民生活的轉變】<br />\n．改革開放發展歷程的概略（重要階段）及相關策略<br />\n．人民生活素質（經濟收入、消費模式、教育程度、醫療、壽命、滅貧等）的提升<br />\n． <strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">綜合國力的提升</span></span></strong>（建立社會主義市場經濟、文化、法治、社會治理、生態文明、教育、科技、國防、體育、基礎建設等）<br />\n<br />\n【國家最新發展與香港融入發展的規劃和政策】<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">．國家最近期的五年發展規劃的重點及相關政策；這些重點和政策與促進國家和香港的關係<br />\n．涉及香港的發展規劃和政策</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【參與國際事務的行動及倡議】<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>．國家自進入 21 世紀以來所形成的全方位外交理念</strong></span><br />\n．<strong><span class=\"red\">「一帶一路」</span></strong>倡議<br />\n<br />\n3 互聯相依的當代世界（45&ndash;50 小時）<br />\n【經濟全球化】<br />\n．各國經濟體系的互相依存和國際經濟組織合作，對香港及國家發展的影響<br />\n<br />\n【科技發展與資訊素養】<br />\n．全球科技新發展（人工智能、大數據、雲端儲存）<br />\n．科技倫理與資訊素養（資訊素養的內涵與正面價值觀的關係；辨別虛假資訊，使用科技的道德操守，遵守相關法律）<br />\n<br />\n【全球環境問題與可持續發展】<br />\n．可持續發展的理念，國家（包括香港）及其他地區的實踐經驗<br />\n<br />\n【公共衛生與人類健康】<br />\n．國家和香港對全球公共衛生的貢獻；國家和非政府組織的援助行動<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊「內地考察」＊＊＊<br />\n【傳統中華文化的特質】<br />\n．網上自學介紹傳統中華文化的特質的文章<br />\n<br />\n【實地考察簡介事項】<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">前往內地考察，體會中華文化在社會的保育與傳承<br />\n．事前詳細計劃及閱覽資料<br />\n．於考察地點搜集資料的方法<br />\n． 撰寫考察報告的要求</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:28:50.000Z","msg":"民族社會主義教育咪算"},{"pid":"960d7a33b4381f42a4de1f37d164a9c9928e2170","tid":2393493,"uid":63183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"呢單大鑊呀"},{"pid":"4a2ad6161dbed3a4e1fc556b113dc9683dd0effc","tid":2393493,"uid":69289,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"跟支共就最好：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img14.360buyimg.com/n1/jfs/t1/86884/3/6726/239177/5df583c8E17ee1f9e/3dcfcc795f3066df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg14.360buyimg.com%2Fn1%2Fjfs%2Ft1%2F86884%2F3%2F6726%2F239177%2F5df583c8E17ee1f9e%2F3dcfcc795f3066df.jpg&h=3d806266&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3648d22db91f834db7cb24191ce0e26ceece5565","tid":2393493,"uid":363016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:33:45.000Z","msg":"改名真係好愚蠢嘅行為"},{"pid":"1ecd2eef2cff04fa2eaee04ad0f03d1e8f2453ee","tid":2393493,"uid":167931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e49c419c3da6197ac93ee88cb62139c49a6bde0","tid":2393493,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"國民教育啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n14年啊那<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推翻啊那<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528ea409146b29b0d13efd15909f43bd2ac7d6f0","tid":2393493,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:35:46.000Z","msg":"叫习學"},{"pid":"dc2e5d2138201e4a9cec8edf2c245c683a020981","tid":2393493,"uid":363016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"等於往屆學生 就算考到5**，日後要rejupas，都當係pass，5**同2冇分別？真係好唔公平，對於重讀嘅同學。<br />\n港共賤畜喪心病狂"},{"pid":"5939fd3f96405b96734dd02091c4117626954d54","tid":2393493,"uid":42250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"(新) 重新冠名科目 = 新冠科"},{"pid":"f346fd5adb707d52381e4df48243f960e5b3aeb1","tid":2393493,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9528efe833b07045d6739ef94fe567414c64a559","tid":2393493,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5939fd3f96405b96734dd02091c4117626954d54","tid":2393493,"uid":42250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"(新) 重新冠名科目 = 新冠科"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:41:00.000Z","msg":"=武漢科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b4019df2bf4d543655f5e15d1249095358144f","tid":2393493,"uid":45003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:41:55.000Z","msg":"習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想學習教育"},{"pid":"9cbc8dfca1c68322f4d5edbced3e3bdb2f435b0d","tid":2393493,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:25:55.000Z","msg":"支持叫國民教育科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccfa111168d64a5fb061a99e891bc42ccef9b55","tid":2393493,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"叫極端民族主義教育"},{"pid":"aebb2727b53164ef95e2562b0af4f65cfcbbcb10","tid":2393493,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:32:40.000Z","msg":"意料中事<br />\n仲驚佢唔做到呢步<br />\n加唔夠燃料<br />\n好彩"}]}